g.text: Reinventing arts for a new generation.

text.tspan: Enjoy the Arts gives anyone aged 35 or younger
free tickets, ongoing discounts, exclusive invita
tions, and insider information to Cincinnati's arts
scene. Prior to this engagement, all of these tickets
were distrubuted via a paper coupon booklet.
The project was completed in a one month time
frame to work within a non-projit budget.
